<h4 id="articlelabel" class="heavyseriflbl heavyseriflblbold sm">Prescriptions</h4>
<h2 id="articletitle" class="regserif entry-title">
Drug costs driving B.C. residents to skip medication, study finds
</h2>
<div id="articlemeta">
<h4 class="heavyseriflbl sm byline author vcard">
<a href="/authors/rod-mickleburgh/" class="hl-gam" title="rod mickleburgh ">rod mickleburgh </a>
</h4>
<h5 class="sans sm updated">
<span class="articleplaceline">VANCOUVER&#8212; </span>
<span class="articlecreditline">From Tuesday's Globe and Mail</span>
</h5>
<h5 class="articledateline sans sm">Published <time pubdate datetime="2012-01-16 22:14 -0500">Monday, Jan. 16, 2012 10:14PM EST</time></h5>
<h5 class="articledateline sans sm">Last updated <time datetime="2012-01-16 22:24 -0500">Monday, Jan. 16, 2012 10:24PM EST</time></h5>
</div>
<aside class="articleseealso articleseealsoheader">
<ul>
</ul>
</aside>
<!-- /seealsotop -->
<div class="articlecommentcountholder heavyserif">
<a href="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/bc-politics/drug-costs-driving-bc-residents-to-skip-medication-study-finds/article2304756/comments/" class="articlecommentcount" title="Go to the comments page">30 comments</a>
<span class="goindicator"></span>
</div>
<ul class="articletoolbar s6of12 sans tiny">
<li class="articleemail">
<a href="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/bc-politics/drug-costs-driving-bc-residents-to-skip-medication-study-finds/article2304756/email/" class="replacedicon" rel="email" title="Email this to a friend">Email</a>
</li>
<li class="articletwitter">
<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/bc-politics/drug-costs-driving-bc-residents-to-skip-medication-study-finds/article2304756/&text=Drug costs driving B.C. residents to skip medication, study finds&via=globeandmail" data-url="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/bc-politics/drug-costs-driving-bc-residents-to-skip-medication-study-finds/article2304756/" data-counturl="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/bc-politics/drug-costs-driving-bc-residents-to-skip-medication-study-finds/article2304756/" data-count="true" data-text="Drug costs driving B.C. residents to skip medication, study finds" data-via="globeandmail" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a>
</li>
<li class="articlefacebook">
